SELECT td.trade_id, td.symbol, th.trade_volume, ma.market_name FROM trade_data td JOIN trade_history th ON td.trade_id = th.trade_id JOIN market_data ma ON th.market_id = ma.market_id WHERE th.trade_volume > 1000 ORDER BY th.trade_volume DESC;

SELECT ta.analytics_id, td.symbol, ta.performance_rating, ta.analysis_date FROM trade_data td JOIN trade_analytics ta ON td.trade_id = ta.trade_id WHERE ta.performance_rating > 8.0 ORDER BY ta.analysis_date DESC;
SELECT mt.trend_id, mt.trend_name, mt.trend_description, td.symbol FROM market_trends mt LEFT JOIN trade_data td ON mt.trend_name = td.symbol WHERE td.symbol IS NULL ORDER BY mt.trend_id ASC;
